{"tid":513793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實香港人唔係政治冷感，而係差緊一個領䄂","createTime":"2017-12-30T02:18:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-31T02:32:37.000Z","uid":6988,"like":67,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"e9e75c4c90331021f5c773076b028c763f7f77e3","tid":513793,"uid":6988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T02:18:39.000Z","msg":"雨革前都係學生領袖搞罷課先引起社會關注 衝公民廣場 加上政府粗暴對待雨革先形成<br />\n今時今日市民已經厭倦所謂遊行 集會<br />\n厭倦出賣過無數次市民嘅販民<br />\n香港人係等緊一個領袖去抗爭<br />\n希望1月1日 你地唔好再講遊行 補選 籌款<br />\n而係佔領 圍堵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c74049bbad48a76b1f31db0f43ccfe5ef7eddacf","tid":513793,"uid":51904,"like":47,"dislike":9,"score":38,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T02:19:44.000Z","msg":"當初有領䄂又話要拆大台<br />\n而家又黎話要一個領䄂<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8be6bf205c8f6393e4915ff42fb4f776e3b63a64","tid":513793,"uid":10672,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T02:22:42.000Z","msg":"大陸實行文化侵略<br />\n到時香港人血統所淨無幾"},{"pid":"48ec4ec2c1d3dcf34a80418f399d564285f5f4f0","tid":513793,"uid":6988,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"c74049bbad48a76b1f31db0f43ccfe5ef7eddacf","tid":513793,"uid":51904,"like":47,"dislike":9,"score":38,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T02:19:44.000Z","msg":"當初有領䄂又話要拆大台<br />\n而家又黎話要一個領䄂<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T02:25:08.000Z","msg":"大部分人都好想出黎<br />\n但奈何販民作風保守 本土派太衝負擔唔起<br />\n大台係佔領之後嘅事<br />\n而家係民心冷淡 咩事都冇人出<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de89560061983183cabf2c976c1663a18852b59f","tid":513793,"uid":132038,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T02:25:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c52b2167d2daecdaf3ea00ec830731a62c3441ac","tid":513793,"uid":132038,"like":3,"dislike":12,"sc